  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "para_id": "Q001050.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Ur-Nanše , king of Lagaš , child of Gunidu , citizen of Gursar , built the Bagara of fired brick . He dug the Bagara .... ...."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001050.17",
      "line_range": "17",
      "translation": "(iii 7) He built the Ebgal . He built the temple of Nanše . He built the shrine of Ĝirsu . He built the Kinir . He built the temple of Ĝatumdug . He built the Tiraš . He built the Nine-ĝara . He built the temple of Ninmarki . He built the E-dam . He built the Kame . He built the Abzu-ega . He built the city wall of Lagaš ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001050.40",
      "line_range": "40",
      "translation": "(v 10) He dug the Pa-saman-canal . He dug the A-suhur-canal ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001050.44",
      "line_range": "44",
      "translation": "(vi 3) He fashioned ( the statue of ) Ninmarki . He fashioned ( the statue of ) Nineš-REC107 . He fashioned ( the statue of ) Ninĝidru . He fashioned ( the statue of ) Šul-šagana . He fashioned ( the statue of ) Kindazid . He fashioned ( the statue of ) Gušudu . He fashioned ( the statue of ) Lama-u-e . He fashioned ( the statue of ) Lugal-urtur ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001050.60",
      "line_range": "60",
      "translation": "(r i 1) The leader of Lagaš went into battle against the leader of Urim and the leader of Umma ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001050.65",
      "line_range": "65",
      "translation": "(r i 6) The leader of Lagaš defeated the leader of Urim , and captured him . He captured the captain of the barges . He captured the captains Ama-barage-si and Kišibĝal . He captured Pap-ursaĝ , child of .... He captured the captains [ ... ] and [ ... ] . He piled up burial mounds ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001050.83",
      "line_range": "83",
      "translation": "(r iii 11) He defeated the leader of Umma . He captured the captains Lupada and Pabilga-lala . He captured Pabilgal-tuku , the ruler of Umma . He captured captain Ur-pusaĝ . He captured chief merchant Hursaĝše-mah . He piled up burial mounds ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001050.101",
      "line_range": "101",
      "translation": "(r vi 7) The leader of Umma ."
    }
  ],
